Here are some notes about tasks to do.

Checking out the Gibson Echoplex pedal
--------------------------------------

Pedals/buttons:
 * record: erase and record new contents to the buffer
 * overdub: over-record in the buffer
 * multiply: change duration to repeat buffer 4 times
 * insert: overwrite a part of a buffer
 * mute: mute this buffer 
 * undo: undo whatever you have just done. (wow)
 * next loop: select next buffer

Set tempo: able to set the tempo using MIDI messages. 

